<li>Simple user-friendly interface</li>
<li>Print origin setting, image resizing</li>
<li>Raster and Vector images support</li>
<li>Repetitive print jobs for industrial applications</li>
<li>Previewing</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Print Engine</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Vivid color reproduction</li>
<li>Bi-directional and Uni-directional print modes</li>
<li>Supports multiple ink channel configurations</li>
<li>Supports different resolution print modes (360x360 and up to 1440x2880dpi)</li>
<li>Support for jpg, tiff, bmp, png, eps and pdf image files</li>
<li>Total ink limit and individual ink channel limit settings</li>
<li>Color management engine with ICC profiles support</li>
<li>Direct printing from common graphic software. (CorelDraw, Photoshop, Autocad...)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
